35dwarf_producer_finish(Dwarf_P_Debug dbg, Dwarf_Error *error)
36{
37
38 if (dbg == NULL || dbg->dbg_mode != DW_DLC_WRITE) {
39 DWARF_SET_ERROR(dbg, error, DW_DLE_ARGUMENT);
40 return (DW_DLV_NOCOUNT);
41 }
42
43 _dwarf_deinit(dbg);
44
45 free(dbg);
46
47 return (1);
48}
